@startuml wizard-flow
skinparam backgroundColor #0f1115
skinparam defaultFontColor #e5e7eb
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam ArrowColor #4fa3ff
skinparam activityBorderColor #252a35
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #181b22
skinparam activityFontColor #e5e7eb
skinparam activityBarColor #4fa3ff
skinparam partitionBorderColor #252a35
skinparam partitionBackgroundColor #181b22

title ILIAD Check-in — Wizard Flow

|User|
start
:Provide source\n(URL / file path);

|System|
:1. **Sniff**\nDetect format\n(NetCDF, CSV, GeoParquet,\nGeoJSON, WFS, EDR, OPeNDAP);

if (format unknown?) then (yes)
  :Abort — cannot classify;
  stop
endif

:2. **Profile**\nExtract properties, dimensions,\nsample values, spatial/temporal extent;

:3. **Match bblocks**\nRank all _sources/* bblocks\n(leaf overlap 45% · path 20%\n· vocab 20% · format 15%);

|User|
:Review ranked bblock list;
:Pick target bblock\nor "generate new";

|System|
:4. **Related bblocks**\nSuggest siblings linked by\nOGC standards (STAC+Coverage,\nEDR+Features, etc.);

:5. **Vocab mapping**\nMatch each property → local index\n(context.jsonld + OIM TTL)\nand present candidates;

|User|
:Acknowledge / adjust\nvocabulary mappings\nPer-property URI selection;

|System|
:6. **Transformer selection**\nFind matching library transformers\n(by input format + canonical output)\nAlways surface json-to-nested-json;

|User|
:Pick transformer;\n:Configure params\n(lon_field, lat_field, …);\n:Set field mappings\n(source path or ${expression} → target path);

|System|
:Run transformer\non sampled data;

if (transformer OK?) then (no)
  |User|
  :Fix mapping / abort?;
  if (abort?) then (yes)
    stop
  else (fix)
    :Adjust mappings;
  endif
  |System|
endif

:7. **Emit staged bblock**\nWrite to _sources/_staging/<id>/\nbblock.json · schema.json\ncontext.jsonld · examples/\ntransforms/ · tests/;

|User|
:Review staged output;

|System|
:8. **Validate** (optional)\nOGC bblocks-postprocess Docker;

|User|
:Promote?;

|System|
:9. **Promote**\nMove _staging/<id>/\n→ _sources/<id>/;

stop
@enduml
